	<Title>
		Do you need sunscreen in the winter?
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;You bet! It&apos;s as easy to get sunburned in winter as in summer. Snow reflects the sun&apos;s rays, so sunburn is possible even if you&apos;re cold. When you&apos;re outdoors in the winter, wear sunscreen on any exposed areas. Use lip balm that contains sunscreen, too.&lt;/p&gt;
	</Body>
